reviewText: I see why the show didn't last......it was neat to see the comics at the beginnings of there careers but the show stunk!!!
I think the CD was better, Snaps: The album Vol 1.  This wasn't too bad.  Pretty short though, only two episodes.

This was on HBO ages ago, but I missed it then.  Finally, I got to see what it was all about.  A younger Tracy Morgan, Mo'Nique, Ricky Smiley, and others go at it.  Best snapping acton I've ever seen!  A keeper.
